```json
{
  "business_hours": null,
  "emergency_triggers": ["live wires"],
  "emergency_transfer_number": "unknown",
  "routing_rules": null
}
```

And `new_transcript_text` contains:

```text
Our business hours are Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm. In case of an emergency, please call 911 or our emergency transfer number, 1-800-EMERGENCY. If you see live wires, please do not approach them. Our routing rules are to transfer all emergency calls to the emergency team.
```

